    <h1>The <span class="blue-t">Melting</span> Ice Cube</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Holding cash isn't a conservative decision. It's an active one — with a quantifiable, ongoing cost. Every treasury is making this choice, whether it knows it or not.</p>
  </header>

